139
00:13:10,415 --> 00:13:11,500
¿Era skinhead?

140
00:13:11,958 --> 00:13:14,044
Digamos que era "el skinhead".

141
00:13:14,252 --> 00:13:16,171
Protegido de Cameron Alexander.

142
00:13:16,421 --> 00:13:17,464
¿Quién?

143
00:13:19,090 --> 00:13:21,176
Aquí está. Echadle una mirada.

144
00:13:22,052 --> 00:13:23,345
Cameron Alexander

145
00:13:23,720 --> 00:13:25,222
es fuerte en Venice Beach.

146
00:13:25,597 --> 00:13:28,975
El mayor distribuidor
de literatura del poder blanco

147
00:13:28,975 --> 00:13:30,018
de Los Angeles.

148
00:13:30,560 --> 00:13:33,396
